ENS domains can be bought and sold on secondary markets.

meta.description: Decentraland is an Ethereum blockchain-powered virtual world, developed and owned by its users, who can create, experience, and monetize content and applications. These unique human-readable names allow users to trade tokens between memorable addresses, e.g. ‘jane.dcl.eth’. In this OpenSea store, you can buy and sell Decentraland Names in MANA, DCL's native currency.

26688630.description:
To celebrate the 4th anniversary of ENS, I created this 6 second animation loop artwork which will be airdropped to 100 winners of the raffle. I wanted to reward those who are active within the crypto community.
